<author>d/ zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, sạmy̱ nʿym</author>
<title>ḥạjty dwmaⁿạ ạ̹lyk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ḥạjty dwmaⁿạ ạ̹lyk ..rạḥty fy rạḥtyk
 kl ạ̉mry fy ydyk .. ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- ḥbyby yạ yswʿ .. ṭbyby yạ yswʿ
 nṣyby yạ yswʿ .. wḥdk mlʾ ạlḍlwʿ
 2- (ḥbk rby ktẖyr .. wạldm ạljạry gẖzyr
 ṣfḥk ʿny kbyr .. ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 3- (lst ạ̉ḥtạj swạk .. qlt ly ạ̉fgẖrn fạk
 ạ̉nt tmlạ̉ ftạk .. ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2
 4- (ạ̉nt sydy ḥbyby .. ạ̉nt ly kẖyr nṣyby
 ạ̉nt ậtiⁿ ʿn qryb .. ḥbyby yạ yswʿ)2</lyrics>
</song>